52
00:05:20.220 --> 00:05:22.620
<i>KADUNUD TAPLUSES</i>

53
00:05:28.520 --> 00:05:31.520
<i>LAWRENCE OPELKA: KAPRAL</i>

54
00:05:32.220 --> 00:05:34.720
<i>KADUNUD TAPLUSES</i>

55
00:05:37.020 --> 00:05:40.720
Hüpake, leitnant.
Ütlesin, hüpake, leitnant.


56
00:05:45.220 --> 00:05:49.120
